{"tid":2320073,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"5 人踢保後再被捕 被控 「暴動」、「暴動時使用蒙面物品」涉去年兆康站抗爭","createTime":"2020-12-10T13:35:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T13:35:24.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7a78caad3ee70e6d91bd355f26e76936b8c4a9c0","tid":2320073,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:35:24.000Z","msg":"今日（10日）警方拘捕 3 男 2 女，他們被指在去年 10 月 7 日破壞屯門兆康西鐵站及輕鐵站，被控「暴動」、「暴動時使用蒙面物品」等罪。<br />\n<br />\n被捕人士年齡介乎 15 至 33 歲，包括一名 15 歲的女學生、兩名 19 歲及 22 歲的大學生、一名 21 歲地產經紀及一名 33 歲的電訊銷售員。所有被捕人士均被起訴「暴動」、「暴動時使用蒙面物品」，其中一男一女另被控「管有物品意圖損壞及破壞財產」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/5-%E4%BA%BA%E8%B8%A2%E4%BF%9D%E5%BE%8C%E5%86%8D%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%BD%AA-%E6%B6%89%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%86%E5%BA%B7%E7%AB%99%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F5-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B8%25A2%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2585%2586%25E5%25BA%25B7%25E7%25AB%2599%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%2F&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqWXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=b063794d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F5-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B8%25A2%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2585%2586%25E5%25BA%25B7%25E7%25AB%2599%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%2F&h=58877f5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/5-%E4%BA%BA%E8%B8%A2%E4%BF%9D%E5%BE%8C%E5%86%8D%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%BD%AA-%E6%B6%89%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%86%E5%BA%B7%E7%AB%99%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD/</a><br />\n<br />\n咁樣分兩條罪告<img src=\"/asse